data.description: Attached home that has just been renovated.  This half-duplex is super-efficient with no HOA or dues and is close to everything!  There are two bedrooms and two full baths.  Back yard is much larger than it appears because it includes much of the woods behind the house which makes for a private and pleasant setting.  Walking distance to Kingsland's Lions Park which features a walking trail, baseball, basketball, skate park, tennis, and Justin's Miracle Field.  Seller is including a 1 year Old Republic Home Warranty for buyer's peace of mind.  Move-in ready.
